'''Aslon Oliveira''' (born 10 January 1994) is an [[India]]n professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[striker (association football)|striker]] for [[Salgaocar F.C.]] in the [[I-League]].

==Career==

===Salgaocar===
Oliveira made his professional debut on 28 April 2014 against [[Churchill Brothers]] at the [[Tilak Maidan Stadium]] in which he came on as a substitute for [[Rosario Mendes]] in the 70th minute as Salgaocar lost the match 1-2.<ref>{{cite web|title=Salgaocar vs. Churchill Brothers 1-2|url=https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2014/04/28/india/i-league/salgaocar-sports-club/churchill-brothers-sc/1585450/|work=Soccerway}}</ref>

